  "title": "CHIEF COOK",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Oversee daily kitchen operations and food preparation</p></li><li><p>Plan menus and ensure food quality, taste, and presentation</p></li><li><p>Supervise, train, and manage kitchen staff</p></li><li><p>Control food cost, inventory, and wastage</p></li><li><p>Ensure kitchen cleanliness and compliance with food hygiene standards</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with management on menu planning and kitchen efficiency</p></li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Proven experience as a Chief Cook / Head Cook</p></li><li><p>Strong knowledge of food preparation and kitchen operations</p></li><li><p>Ability to manage a kitchen team efficiently</p></li><li><p>Familiar with food safety and hygiene regulations</p></li><li><p>Able to work under pressure and long hours</p></li><li><p>Responsible, disciplined, and leadership skills required</p></li></ul>",
